---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import BlogEntries from "@/components/BlogEntry.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <section>
    <div class="py-24">
      <h1
        class="text-4xl text-balance font-medium font-display text-base-900"
      >
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-base-500 mt-4">
        Last Updated: <time datetime="2026-04-30">April 30, 2026</time>
      </p>
    <div class="space-y-12 text-base-600 leading-relaxed mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base-900 mb-4">Data Collection & Tracking</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          This Website does <strong class="text-base-800">not</strong> directly collect personal data, use cookies, or run analytics. However, when you access this website, technical data such as your IP address and request metadata may be processed by infrastructure providers (see below). This processing is necessary to deliver the website securely and reliably (legitimate interest).
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base-900 mb-4">Infrastructure & Third-Parties</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          This website is hosted on GitHub and delivered via Cloudflare. These providers may process technical data (e.g., IP address, user agent) as part of their services. Be aware these providers may process data outside the European Union in accordance with their safeguards. I do not access or store this data myself. See their respective privacy policy for more information on how they may handle your data.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-base-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-base-100">
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li>
              <span class="block font-medium text-base-900">GitHub (Hosting)</span>
              <span class="block text-sm">Content delivery and server security.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="block font-medium text-base-900">Cloudflare (CDN)</span>
              <span class="block text-sm">Performance optimization and threat protection.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="block font-medium text-base-900">rsms.me (Font)</span>
              <span class="block text-sm">Serves the Inter font family.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base-900 mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          I do not retain personal data. Third-party providers may retain technical logs according to their own policies.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base-900 mb-4">External Links</h2>
        <p>
          Content on this site may link to external websites. Those third parties control their own processing of data. I am not responsible for the privacy practices of external websites.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base-900 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Under GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, or delete your personal data, as well as to restrict or object to its processing. You also have the right to lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base-900 mb-4">Data Controller</h2>
        <p>
          Nicolas Jaroussie - hello [at] jacra.me. If you have questions about this policy, do not hesitate to contact me. I will use only the information you provide to respond to your message.
        </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
